{"tid":740872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩男生涉偷拍88女生更衣及裙底 辯方質疑事發後老師未有通知家長","createTime":"2018-07-13T08:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T09:03:57.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dcbb49e25e1f4d279b9ab95f486a93c18c2792bc","tid":740872,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T08:19:17.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】港島區名校校內偷拍案，有男學生涉嫌利用運動錄影器材在運動場、泳池偷拍女生更衣，更在課室地板放置Ipad偷錄裙底，涉案的受害女生達88人。兩名不認罪的被告今於東區裁判法院少年法庭繼續審訊，繼續傳召證人作供。<br />\n<br />\n昨日的審訊中辯方質疑教師對被告進行逼供，包括不准進食、如廁，又指出老師曾不准學生使用手機及聯絡家長。今日辯方繼續就老師調查事件的手法盤問證人，辯方指出在2017年3月24日發現事件後一直沒有通知家長，並且沒收被告手機，直到同月27日老師在學校考試後再次要求相關學生填寫口供，其中第二被告填寫完口供後被單獨帶到教員室，一名訓導主任要求他為自己的手機解鎖並查看他的相簿及Whatsapp對話紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n另外，訓導主任再次強調是需要釐清事件再通知家長，但辯方指出27日下午，他的通話紀錄中顯示第二被告的父親曾經致電給他，但通話時間只有3至4秒，他指當時可能正在處理公務所以未能接聽。但其後Whatsapp紀錄顯示父親有傳送訊息請他回電，但訓導主任也沒有回電，同日稍後時間被告在學校被拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n案件於下午續審，控方將傳召更多證人作供。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%A9%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F%E6%B6%89%E5%81%B7%E6%8B%8D88%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E6%9B%B4%E8%A1%A3%E5%8F%8A%E8%A3%99%E5%BA%95-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E4%BA%8B%E7%99%BC%E5%BE%8C%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E6%9C%AA%E6%9C%89%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E5%AE%B6%E9%95%B7-043600171.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%2581%25B7%25E6%258B%258D88%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259B%25B4%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E5%258F%258A%25E8%25A3%2599%25E5%25BA%2595-%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E4%25BA%258B%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%259F%25A5%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7-043600171.html&d=RMO9wrFjHlowV%2BoHQbAkzk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=588ace41\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%A9%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F%E6%B6%89%E5%81%B7%E6%8B%8D88%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E6%9B%B4%E8%A1%A3%E5%8F%8A%E8%A3%99%E5%BA%95-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E4%BA%8B%E7%99%BC%E5%BE%8C%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E6%9C%AA%E6%9C%89%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E5%AE%B6%E9%95%B7-043600171.html</a>"},{"pid":"bb243f1954af0fb9c1cf8f10b54bd59d65366f0b","tid":740872,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T08:23:26.000Z","msg":"獨樂樂不如眾樂樂<br />\n知左梗係睇埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93946341bb79052d63df1ebd6a9956280943841a","tid":740872,"uid":174601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T08:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登 公海"},{"pid":"8837df134d0750193fb27b357ca8868062768993","tid":740872,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T08:29:10.000Z","msg":"邊間名校？"},{"pid":"9c3c0eabd58bd5628e24a19ab143d42c965dd8ea","tid":740872,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8837df134d0750193fb27b357ca8868062768993","tid":740872,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T08:29:10.000Z","msg":"邊間名校？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T08:36:07.000Z","msg":"男女校<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00289cb0c04c7b5f367b79228599f3b842e3010","tid":740872,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c3c0eabd58bd5628e24a19ab143d42c965dd8ea","tid":740872,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8837df134d0750193fb27b357ca8868062768993","tid":740872,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T08:29:10.000Z","msg":"邊間名校？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T08:36:07.000Z","msg":"男女校<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T08:45:28.000Z","msg":"好似係2017-2018呢屆嘅中三<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/red.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8264a1da101a8bc64df4466dde428d35766beb5","tid":740872,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T09:03:57.000Z","msg":"當年中學都算係名校，有條友仔借人電話玩（個陣未個個有電話），點知條仆街仔比人斷正貼女同學裙低。條友仲想屈借機比佢個同學仔<br />\n<br />\n女同學家長想報驚<br />\n垃圾校長驚上報影響校譽，局家長唔比報<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，條友仔而家係醫生，諗起睇佢既女病人就慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}